data.description: This beautiful pool home offers lots of upgrades. An Open kitchen with a lot of counter space and a breakfast nook, All the formal rooms, a Master bedroom suite located on the first floor, 3 bedrooms, and 2 baths upstairs with a huge bonus room/loft. This is An Oversized/Conservation Lot with tranquility and wildlife surrounding you. Minutes away from Disney Parks, Beaches, and The Loop Mall.
